{"tid":1979810,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"想死，有冇黃嘅精神科醫生","createTime":"2020-04-19T16:31:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-26T10:20:03.000Z","uid":114949,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0a736fcc3b671a8fd94872c17b27bc1fc245dc52","tid":1979810,"uid":114949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:31:09.000Z","msg":"曾經睇過一位醫生，感覺中規中矩。診所離屋企太遠，搭車要兩個鐘左右，小弟唔知係因為病定太離地唔係好鐘意搭車，感覺好辛苦。加上嗰陣未儲到錢唔想用屋企人錢睇病同埋感覺有漸漸變好就冇去繼續睇。<br />\n<br />\n最近病情好似嚴重翻，讀書同人際關係都受到更嚴重影響，所以想搵個好嘅醫生睇，希望可以好翻。<br />\n<br />\n想搵黃嘅醫生係因為驚藍嘅會一句後生仔唔捱得收咗我皮（physically and mentally)同埋驚講錯嘢（u know what I mean)，所以希望有人可以介紹一位黃嘅醫生比我。<br />\n<br />\n係情神科醫生唔係心理醫生，需要食藥只有情神科醫生可以處方。<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n唔刻各位<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8206d4d84c9078bd7effeee8b7ec8bb71eb921b","tid":1979810,"uid":155725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:37:07.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"de4741b9bc89164094d3683913770d607d9678df","tid":1979810,"uid":304141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:40:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"49edecd7e515e9eeb857dbae0e263127583782d2","tid":1979810,"uid":134431,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:41:14.000Z","msg":"試下冬菇醫院門診... 算好多黃"},{"pid":"92582b2f83cb73cb5d2892415c0c19fc15a20f72","tid":1979810,"uid":75394,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:44:49.000Z","msg":"Search 下之前聯署過黃嘅醫生"},{"pid":"7610a9a933357d29e139be19081c060ae510d9ac","tid":1979810,"uid":114949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de4741b9bc89164094d3683913770d607d9678df","tid":1979810,"uid":304141,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:40:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T18:45:51.000Z","msg":"試吓搵社工傾下？"},{"pid":"87a929d6218c6e6418054d1e15f1d7bd07238eaa","tid":1979810,"uid":114949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc